subject: Bicycles and Bicycling
Doping (Sports)
lead_paragraph: Alberto Contador won won the 7.7-mile time trial in Murcia, Spain, and won the three-day race by 11 seconds in 9 hours 27 minutes 18 seconds. Jerome Coppel of France was second.
